  POST /generation/{usecase_id}/{pipeline_id}
  Header : AMToken = <JWT>
  Body   : { "query": "...", "history": [{"question":"...","answer":"..."}] }
  Answer : response["data"]["content"]["content"]

JWT: OpenAM → SSO tokenId → JWT via tokenTranslator_v2 (30s TTL, auto-refresh 25s)

Install:
  pip install streamlit requests httpx truststore python-dotenv
  streamlit run genie_bot_streamlit_poc.py
"""

